#

Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Garlic Mashed Cauliflower and Steamed Asparagus

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carbhigh-protein

Tags:

grilledhealthylow-carbgourmet

Description

A zesty and succulent grilled chicken dish paired with creamy garlic mashed cauliflower and vibrant steamed asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 2 (6 oz) pieces
  • Lemon Juice: 3 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Fresh Rosemary: 1 tbsp
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tbsp
  • Cauliflower: 1 medium head
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
